## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the topic. The sources used vary in their academic rigor, and some may present subjective viewpoints. Additionally, the report does not cover potential positive aspects of stereotyping, as the focus was specifically on negative effects. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.